quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  81,1,"When the sun is wrapped up [in darkness]"
  81,2,"And when the stars fall, dispersing,"
  81,3,"And when the mountains are removed"
  81,4,"And when full-term she-camels{1} are neglected",footnotes:1:1
  81,5,"And when the wild beasts are gathered"
  81,6,"And when the seas are filled with flame{1}",footnotes:1:1
  81,7,"And when the souls are paired{1}",footnotes:1:1
  81,8,"And when the girl [who was] buried alive is asked"
  81,9,"For what sin she was killed"
  81,10,"And when the pages{1} are spread [i.e., made public]",footnotes:1:1